id: 63
event: agent
data: {"type":"text_delta","delta":"The live site is a Squarespace hospitality page with a tight set of facts: Eagle Street Brisbane, Greek celebration positioning, bookings via SevenRooms, menu/function/gift-voucher/gallery/contact intent, and menu highlights like Ocean Trout, Lamb Shoulder, Keftedes, Kokkinisto, Bougatsa, and Haloumi Chips. I’m pulling the source styling and media references now so the concept feels matched rather than generic."}

